      "span_text": "Poly(butyl acrylate) (PBA, Mw: 72,700 g/mol), poly(2-(2-methoxyethoxy) ethyl acrylate-co-butyl acrylate) (30:70 mol%, PMe2A, Mw: 40,500 g/mol) and poly(2-(2-methoxyethoxy) ethoxy ethyl acrylate-co-butyl acrylate) (30:70 mol%, PMe3A, Mw: 35,600 g/mol) were also synthesized as described in a previous report [CITATION_3] ."
